1)	Write a program to check if a string is palindrome.

Code:

string=input("enter string")
left=0
right=len(string)-1
palindrome=True
while left<right:
    if string[left]!=string[right]:
        palindrome=False
        break;
    left=left+1
    right=right-1
if palindrome:
    print("palindrome")
else:
    print("Not a palindrome")

output:

